# HTML page title
;How to block annoying ads using an ad blocker
Como blocar enoiose avisos publicitari per un blocator


# HTML page description
;How to stop seeing too many ads and keep companies from following you around online. An ad blocker guide from the Firefox web browser.
Como cessar de vider trop avisos publicitari e impedir al companias de te traciar online. Ab Firefox, le navigator del Web, un guida al blocator de avisos publicitari.


;The ad blocker – a secret weapon against annoying ads.
Le blocator de avisos publicitari – un arma secrete contra enoiose avisos publicitari.


;So many ads, so little patience… It’s time to stop the madness.
Tante avisos publicitari, assi parve patientia… Il es tempore de cessar le follia.


;The average person sees an average of 4,000 ads a day. If you think that’s too many, an ad blocker is your new best friend.
Le persona medie vide un media de 4,000 avisos publicitari in un die. Si tu pensa que illos es trop, un blocator de avisos publicitari es tu nove melior amico.


;An ad blocker is a piece of software that can be used to block ads, and they work in two ways. The first way is when an ad blocker blocks the signal from an advertiser’s server, so the ad never shows up on your page. Another way ad blockers work is by blocking out sections of a website that could be ads.
Un blocator de avisos publicitari es un pecia de software que pote ser usate pro blocar avisos publicitari e labora in duo manieras. Le prime maniera es quando un blocator de avisos publicitari bloca le signal ex un servitor de publicitate, assi le avisos publicitari jammais apparera sur tu pagina. Un altere maniera blocatores de avisos publicitari labora es per blocar sectiones de un sito web que poterea ser avisos publicitari.


;These ads might be loud video ads, ads that follow you around the web, trackers, third-party cookies, and more. To use an ad blocker, you can search for ad blocker add-ons that are available in your browser. <a href="%(firefox)s">Firefox</a>, for example, has <a href="%(addons)s">this list of approved ad blocker add-ons</a>. Click on this list (or ad blockers that are approved for your browser) and see which fits your needs.
Iste avisos publicitari pote ser video a alte volumine, avisos publicitari que te seque circum le Web, traciatores, cookies de tertie-parte, e altero ancora. Pro usar un blocator de avisos publicitari, tu pote cercar ille typo de additivos disponibile in tu navigator. <a href="%(firefox)s">Firefox</a>, per exemplo, ha <a href="%(addons)s">iste lista de additivos blocator approbate</a>. Clicca sur iste lista (o illo del blocatores approbate pro tu navigator) e vide qual adhere a tu requisitos.


;Find the right ad blocker for you
Trova le blocator de avisos publicitari juste pro te


;There’s <a href="%(url)s">AdBlocker Ultimate</a> that gets rid of every single ad, but buyer beware. Some of your favorite newspapers and magazines rely on advertising. Too many people blocking their ads could put them out of business.
Il ha <a href="%(url)s">AdBlocker Ultimate</a> que libera de cata aviso publicitari, ma presta attention comprator. Parte de tu favorite jornales e magazines conta sur le publicitate. Trop personas blocante lor avisos publicitari poterea poner los foras de negotios.


;Popup ads are the worst. Block them with <a href="%(url)s">Popup Blocker</a> and never deal with another annoying popup again.
Le messages publicitari emergente es le pejor. Bloca los con <a href="%(url)s">Popup Blocker</a> e jammais plus tu debera patir lor enoios.


;One of the most popular ad blockers for Chrome, Safari and Firefox is <a href="%(url)s">AdBlock</a>. Use it to block ads on Facebook, YouTube and Hulu.
Un del plus popular blocatores de avisos publicitari pro Chrome, Safari e Firefox es <a href="%(url)s">AdBlock</a>. Usa lo pro blocar avisos publicitari sur Facebook, YouTube e Hulu.


# A tracker-free zone means a no tracker zone.
;Create a tracker-free zone with Content Blocking
Crea un zona franc ab traciatores con Content Blocking


;On Firefox, you can use <a href="%(privacy)s">Privacy</a> or <a href="%(blocking)s">Content Blocking</a> settings to get even more control over ad trackers that serve you the ads.
Sur Firefox, tu pote usar le parametros de <a href="%(privacy)s">Privacy</a> o <a href="%(blocking)s">Content Blocking</a> pro obtener mesmo major controlo sur le traciatores publicitari que te provide los.


;Choose your level of protection
Elige tu nivello de protection


;To start, click on the Firefox menu in the top right-hand corner of your screen. It looks like three lines stacked on top of each other. In the drop-down menu, click on Content Blocking. You should see a blue pop-up with different selections.
Comencia cliccar sur le menu de Firefox in le angulo in alto a dextera de tu schermo. Il pare como tres lineas impilate le un supra le altere. In le menu a tenta, clicca sur Content Blocking. Tu deberea vider un message emergente con differente selectiones.


;Go easy with Standard mode
Va facile con le modo standard


;If ads don’t bother you and you don’t mind being followed by trackers and third-party cookies, then the Standard setting should work for you. To get trackers off your tail in Standard mode, use a <a href="%(url)s">Private Browsing</a> window.
Si le avisos publicitari non te enoia e non te preoccupa esser sequite per traciatores e cookies de tertie-parte, alora le configuration Standard deberea functionar pro te.  Pro tener le traciatores foras de tu cauda in modo Standard, usa un fenestra de <a href="%(url)s">Navigation reservate</a>.


;Get tough with Strict mode
Deveni intransigente con le nivello Restrictive


;If seeing too many ads ruins your day, then the Strict mode is a better fit. This mode will block known third-party trackers and cookies in all Firefox windows.
Si vider trop avisos publicitari ruina tu die, alora le modo Restrictive es un solution melior. Iste modo blocara note traciatores e cookies de tertie-parte in tote le fenestras de Firefox.


;Do-it-yourself Custom mode
Face lo tu mesme: modo Personalisate


;The Custom setting gives you the ultimate choice. You can decide what you’re blocking, including trackers, cookies and more. If you allow cookies from a website, you’ll automatically be in Custom mode.
Le configuration Personalisate te da le selection definitive. Tu pote decider lo que blocar: traciatores, cookies e altero ancora. Si tu permitte cookies ex un sito web, tu sera automaticamente in modo Personalisate.


# ’Cover your trail’ means cover your browsing history.
;Cover your trail, block trackers
Coperi tu pista, bloca traciatores


;Click on the Trackers box and you’ll be able to block trackers in two ways. One way to block trackers is to do it when you’re working in a Private Window. Another way to do it is to block trackers in all windows. Keep in mind that if you choose to always block trackers, some pages might not load correctly.
Clicca sur le quadrato Traciatores e tu potera blocar traciatores in duo manieras. Un maniera de blocar traciatores es laborar in un Fenestra reservate. Un altere maniera de lo facer es blocar le traciatores in tote le fenestras.Tene in mente que si tu elige de blocar sempre le traciatores, alcun paginas pote non cargar correctemente.


;Take a bite out of cookies
Proba le cookies


;<a href="%(url)s">Cookies</a> are sent by websites you visit. They live on your computer and monitor what you’ve been doing on a site. When an airline hikes your rates because you’ve looked at plane tickets once that day, that is the handiwork of a cookie.
Le <a href="%(url)s">cookies</a> es inviate ab le sitos web que tu visita. Illos vive sur tu computator e controla lo que tu ha facite sur un sito. Quando un compania aeree augmenta tu tarifas solo perque tu ha reguardate un vice billetes de aeroplano ille die, isto es obra de un cookie.


;In Firefox, you can block all third-party cookies or just those set by trackers. Be aware that blocking all cookies can break some sites.
In Firefox, tu pote blocar tote le cookies de tertie-parte o solo illos que es configurate per le traciatores. Que tu es conscie que blocar tote le cookies pote rumper alcun sitos.


;Send a Do Not Track signal
Invia un signal Non traciar


# ’Thanks but no thanks’ here means to reject ads.
;If you don’t want your online behavior used for ads, you can send websites a polite “thanks but no thanks” letter by checking the <a href="%(url)s">Do Not Track</a> option of Firefox. Participation is voluntary, but the websites that participate will stop tracking you immediately.
Si tu non vole que tu comportamento online sia usate pro avisos publicitari, tu pote inviar al sitos web un cortese littera de “gratias, ma: no gratias”, marcante le option <a href="%(url)s">Non traciar</a> de Firefox. Participation es voluntari, ma le sitos web que participa cessara de traciar te immediatemente.


;Speed up thanks to ad blockers
Accelerar gratias a blocatores de avisos publicitari


;In some cases, an ad blocker can help your browser go faster. When an ad is loading, it can slow down a website. At the same time, it takes longer to find what you’re looking for if you’re too busy closing yet another ad.
In alcun casos, un blocator de avisos publicitari pote adjutar tu navigator ir plus veloce. Quando un aviso publicitari se carga pote relentar un sito web. In addition, prende plus tempore trovar lo que tu cerca si tu es troppo occupate pro clauder plure avisos publicitari.


;If you want to learn more about ad blocking, there are hundreds of ad blocker extensions available for Firefox and other browsers. If want to try out the ad blockers Firefox uses, <a href="%(url)s">click here to download</a> a browser that puts privacy first.
Si tu desira saper plus re blocada del avisos publicitari, il ha centenas de extensiones blocator de avisos publicitari disponibile pro Firefox e altere navigatores. Si tu vole provar le blocatores de avisos publicitari que usa Firefox, <a href="%(url)s">clicca ci pro discargar</a> un navigator que antepone le confidentialitate.


;Take control of your browser.
Prende controlo de tu navigator.


